value.0: This statue depicts Talos, The Destroyer. He attracts the destroyer, the raider, the looter and the brigand. He is the dark side of nature, the uncaring force waiting to strike at any time.
This fine Calishite style was employed by those hunting and taking leisure away from Calimshan.
A spear consecrated in the rituals of Talos, The Destroyer.
